tron beam at the pc-scale\nregion and fit to the flaring spectrum of 4C +21.35. Detection of >~100 TeV\nneutrinos from 4C +21.35 or other VHE blazars with IceCube or KM3NeT would\nconfirm this scenario.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 29 Mar 2012 14:55:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 5 Jul 2012 15:22:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-04"}
